<h2>Ben Banker at 0x888 Agency</h2>
<p>The 0x888 Agency proudly presents its latest featured artist, Ben Banker, a multidisciplinary creator hailing from Chicago and currently residing in Madison, WI. Boasting a BFA from the prestigious School of the Art Institute and over two decades of experience in both digital art and traditional painting, Banker is a true master of his craft.</p>
<p>Banker's artistic journey has taken him on extensive travels throughout the United States, Canada, and Europe, where he has immersed himself in the rich cultural offerings of world-class museums and galleries. It was during his time at the Art Institute of Chicago, however, that Banker honed his skills and studied the masters up close, spending countless hours poring over paintings with a discerning eye.</p>
<p>With a talent for web design and digital art, Banker has embraced the exciting new frontiers of the NFT realm and the rapidly growing phenomenon of AI art. His work pushes the boundaries of what is possible, while always remaining true to his artistic vision.</p>
<h2>About 0x888 Agency</h2>
<p>The 0x888 Agency is at the forefront of promoting unconventional art and music through its global platform, and Banker is a valued member of its community. As a teacher at our art school, he helps aspiring creators to develop their skills and achieve their artistic goals, inspiring the next generation of talented artists to follow in his footsteps.</p>
